    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "早いな渚。どうしたんだ？　新曲のジャケット撮影の\n打ち合わせの時間まで、まだ二時間もあるけど",
      "startTime": 7.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、午前中のお仕事が凄くスムーズにいって\n予定より早く上がれたんです",
      "startTime": 15,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、新曲の撮影が楽しみ過ぎて\nつい早く来ちゃいました……えへへ",
      "startTime": 20.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、じゃあお茶でも飲んで\nゆっくりしていてくれ……はぁ",
      "startTime": 27.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "？　{user}さん、どうしたんですか？\n元気がないみたいですけど",
      "startTime": 36.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "年末でお忙しいのは分かりますけど\nちゃんとお休みも取って下さいね",
      "startTime": 41.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "元気がないように見えるか？\n表情には出さないようにしてたんだけど……",
      "startTime": 47,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、すぐに分かりますよ",
      "startTime": 50.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_06_01-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "だって、ずっと{user}さんと\n仕事してきたんですから",
      "startTime": 55.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}